{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_01_01",
  "title": "サニーピース 01 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "coast_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事で星見の海に来られるなんて嬉しいなぁ\n今日のロケ、楽しみだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so happy to be able to come to the Hoshimi beach for work.\nI'm looking forward to today's shoot~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.135011358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "こんな風に海辺を散歩するのも久しぶりだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while since we've taken a walk along the beach like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3666666667,
      "endTime": 12.5319501559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "星見の寮にいた頃は、よくみんなで\n海沿いをランニングしたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we were at the dorm in Hoshimi‚ we often went\nrunning along the beach together‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7100908279,
      "endTime": 18.003529682699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃の私は体力がなくて\nいつもお姉ちゃんに迷惑を掛けてたなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't have much stamina back then‚\nso I was always slowing Saki-chan down…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2100908279,
      "endTime": 25.007454863699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんって言えば、この間、千紗ちゃんと一緒に\n雑誌のインタビューを受けてたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of Saki-chan‚ you did a magazine interview\nwith her recently‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1979594548,
      "endTime": 31.648354269600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "『姉妹アイドルの素顔』っていうタイトルで\n二人のプライベートについて話したんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was titled \"The Real Faces of the Sister Idols\"‚\nand you talked about your private lives‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8312927882,
      "endTime": 37.9462985559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、私達の普段の様子とか……\n子供の頃の写真を見ながら昔話をしたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we talked about our usual routine and…\nlooked back on old times while looking at childhood photos.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1646261215,
      "endTime": 45.657741161699995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ちっちゃい頃の千紗ちゃんかぁ……\nきっと可愛かったんだろうなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Little Chisa‚ huh…\nYou must have been cute~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9003633181,
      "endTime": 51.7646172967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "写真ならスマホに入ってるけど……見る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have some photos on my phone… Want to see?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9670299847,
      "endTime": 55.992494805599996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　見たい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I want to see!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.203968811,
      "endTime": 57.8639234066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ、可愛い～！　ちっちゃい千紗ちゃんと\nちっちゃい沙季ちゃんが抱き合ってお昼寝してる～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aww‚ so cute~! Little Chisa and\nlittle Saki are cuddling and taking a nap~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1706354777,
      "endTime": 70.3415168253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんが千紗ちゃんをぎゅーってしてるよ\nこの頃からお姉さんしてたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan is hugging Chisa tightly.\nShe was already acting like an older sister back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5706354777,
      "endTime": 77.2327859467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "は、恥ずかしいから、大きな声で言わないで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-stop it‚ don't say it so loudly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4373021443,
      "endTime": 81.84546550110001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "この写真は……公園で遊んでるのかな？\n千紗ちゃんが楽しそうに笑いながら走ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This photo… are you playing in the park?\nChisa is running around happily‚ laughing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2666666667,
      "endTime": 90.8464511355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "こっちの写真では\n千紗ちゃんが縫い物をしてるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this one‚\nChisa is sewing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3,
      "endTime": 95.4676806218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "私は昔から裁縫が好きで\nお気に入りのお人形の衣装を自分で作ったりしてたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've loved sewing since I was little.\nI used to make clothes for my favorite dolls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8666666667,
      "endTime": 102.87976086709999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "好きなアイドルの衣装を参考にして\nお人形の服を作ったこともあったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even made doll clothes\nbased on my favorite idol's outfits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0666666667,
      "endTime": 108.8591010663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ～。もしかしたら、それが千紗ちゃんが\nファッションに詳しくなるきっかけだったのかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hee~. Maybe that's how you\nbecame interested in fashion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1,
      "endTime": 116.6646216861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "次の写真は……家族でテレビを観てるところかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next photo… is that you watching TV with your family?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9,
      "endTime": 122.06888885500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "それは、お父さんとお姉ちゃんと一緒に\nホラー映画を観てる写真だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That one is from when I was watching a horror movie\nwith Dad and Saki-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2666666667,
      "endTime": 128.13735277499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんはお父さんに抱きついて泣いてるのに\n千紗ちゃんは目をキラキラさせて喜んでるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan is clinging to her dad and crying‚\nbut Chisa is excited‚ with her eyes sparkling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3333333333,
      "endTime": 135.13670100430002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "どの写真でも千紗ちゃんは笑ってて\nとっても楽しそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're smiling in every photo‚ Chisa‚\nand you look so happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3333333333,
      "endTime": 139.68866994520002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、こんなに元気はつらつなのは意外かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's surprising to see you so full of energy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9,
      "endTime": 144.1710657597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "今の私とイメージが違ってて驚くよね\n小さい頃は活発な子供だったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're surprised because it's different from how I am now‚ right?\nI was an active child when I was little…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3666666667,
      "endTime": 153.43306196519998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "（昔の私は、目を離すとすぐにどこかへ）\n（行っちゃうような、やんちゃな子供だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Back then‚ I was a mischievous child who would)\n(run off somewhere.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6666666667,
      "endTime": 161.4971255809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "（そんな私が内気で大人しい性格になったのは）\n（あの出来事がきっかけだった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(What made me become shy and quiet)\n(was that incident…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.7,
      "endTime": 168.76496693040002,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 169
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "（あの日、家族と海水浴に来た私は）\n（お姉ちゃんと一緒に砂浜で遊んでいた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(That day‚ I went to the beach with my family‚)\n(and I was playing on the beach with my sister.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.1,
      "endTime": 178.74612970869998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16333.333333300005,
          "startTime": 187.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
